/>\n圖片來源：維基共享資源<br />\n我們現在的影視劇，春秋戰國時代炮火連天、炸藥橫飛，那是在穿越，或是在戲說，或者乾脆就是偽造歷史。真正導致軍事變革並對歷史起到了重大推動作用的火藥是「黃火藥」，它大規模地用於工程和軍事，是整個近現代軍事工業的奠基石。<br />\n<br />\n「黃火藥」跟「黑火藥」之間完全沒有任何傳承關係，可以說各自平行發展，但得承認，歐洲的「黃火藥」比中國的「黑火藥」出現得更早。<br />\n<br />\n張藝謀的電影《長城》實際上是在誤導觀眾。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T02:40:57.000Z","msg":"呢個係亂噏<br />\n希臘時代無任何有爆炸力既發明<br />\n有的話，都一早延伸發明槍炮"},{"pid":"7238e5ebc41fd4c146a6c897286be509b8877cfa","tid":1889971,"uid":61280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af0651b539346bdd9c8845dc5d025f00e7b3614a","tid":1889971,"uid":522,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T02:21:59.000Z","msg":"中國 = 五千年造假大國"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T02:47:27.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">支狗DNA：<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n自慰當智慧！！！</span></span></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"a376a305613f989fc363cac708e019687c15b71d","tid":1889971,"uid":5303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07bac2ba38256f78143a3365026db4704a213163","tid":1889971,"uid":117276,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T02:25:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/540/https://na.cx/i/YXY9WdA.png\" /><br />\n諗起呢位巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔知佢仲有冇上高登<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T02:48:44.000Z","msg":"可能變左藍絲"},{"pid":"19f2dbf753dc327565ea82f75a2af306982ae0f6","tid":1889971,"uid":58609,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"75a2e168f1c40115d5431852c3cbea31c6ffe28e","tid":1889971,"uid":118346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-21T02:07:05.000Z","msg":"二、火藥<br />\n古